{"tid":1159611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(親中) 日本政府: 美國禁止華為, 將波及日本經濟","createTime":"2019-05-17T23:18:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T11:50:48.000Z","uid":134071,"like":6,"dislike":55,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"735b4151695973574f86ad3ac2af051c82c64ec1","tid":1159611,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T23:18:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.941982/3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Faafn-news%2FNOW.941982%2F3&d=LRk9npnliL4HefRMP%2BWOkNey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=68c33ce8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.941982/3</a><br />\n<br />\n日本財相：美國禁止華為將波及日本經濟<br />\n2019/05/17 14:43<br />\n<br />\n日本財務大臣麻生太郎表示，美國禁止華為購買美國關鍵技術的做法可能影響日本企業，並衝擊經濟增長。他指部分日本企業向華為供應零部件，供應鏈錯綜複雜，可能對日本經濟產生直接或間接影響。<br />\n<br />\n美國商務部昨日(16日)正式將華為及其在20多個國家的68家分支機構列入實體名單，華為須在美國政府批准下從美國公司購買零部件。(fc/t)"},{"pid":"b3090e0257bc8c62508a78b96c2199d8299fa517","tid":1159611,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T23:19:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1457988-20190517.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1457988-20190517.htm&d=LRk9npnliL4HefRMP%2BWOkNey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=1dc43338\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1457988-20190517.htm&h=93741fc9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1457988-20190517.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n 麻生太郎：美國對華為禁令或影響日本經濟<br />\n2019-05-17 HKT 10:27<br />\n<br />\n日本財務大臣麻生太郎表示，美國針對華為禁令，可能影響到日本企業，令經濟受到直接或間接拖累。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，有日本企業向華為供應零部件，相關供應鏈錯綜複雜。<br />\n<br />\n另外，他提到，日本內需及經濟基本面穩健，而低利率及人口減少令地區銀行盈利受壓，認為銀行要由傳統業務獲利越來越困難，要更努力整頓業務模式。"},{"pid":"e12435170b952266c7f52f8d04bd91d433309866","tid":1159611,"uid":61748,"like":6,"disli